EntityDateTimePublicApiCheck - Class in se.mithlond.codestyle.codestyle.checks
Calendar check which should be applied to model projects, implying two rules: The pre-JDK8 time types (Calendar, Date and GregorianCalendar) should not be used in the public API of a class or interface.
